</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A battered wife -- she didn't leave because she was afraid "he'd hurt me or 
kill me." 
</P>
<P>
An abused son -- Evel kicked him in the face. "He looks a lot better with the 
new face. I did it for no charge." 
</P>
<P>
Probable alcoholic -- "knocking back one Canadian Club after another chasing 
them with a Lite beer." 
</P>
<P>
He is Evil!! Evil!! Evil!! 
</P>
<P>
MARY B. MASCHAL 
</P>
