<HEADLINE>
<P>
DUNNING HOUSE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Please encourage anyone who is involved with the Dunning house to let it 
remain. Bend requirements, if necessary, to have it declared a "historic" 
house. So what, if it isn't really. 
</P>
<P>
There is so little of the past that remains in the disposable society of today. 
I love to drive by older, well-kept houses. Not everything in Los Angeles needs 
to be new and palatial. 
</P>
<P>
BARBARA S. WINDT 
</P>
<P>
Los Angeles 
</P>
</TEXT>
