</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By KIM UPTON 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Readers who have been unable to find the books "Farm, Ranch &amp; Country 
Vacations," "Adventure Travel North America" and "Adventure Travel Abroad," can 
obtain them for 12 each (or $13 first-class mail) from Pat Dickerman, Adventure 
Guides Inc., 36 E. 57th St., No. 5L, New York 10022. Phone (212) 355-6334. She 
