HEALTH; NUTRITION; DIET; FAT; POLITICS; SPECIAL INTEREST GROUPS; DEPARTMENT OF 
AGRICULTURE (U.S.); DAIRY INDUSTRY; FOOD INDUSTRY 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA042389-0080 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 47733 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
April 23, 1989, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part 1; Page 1; Column 3; National Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
