</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
TAKESHITA, NOBORU; BRIBERY; RECRUIT CO; POLITICAL CONTRIBUTIONS; JAPAN -- 
GOVERNMENT OFFICIALS; CONFLICT OF INTEREST 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
