puck during Calgary's 5-2 victory Saturday night. ; Photo, (San Diego County 
Edition) Ron Duguay (right) and the Kings couldn't keep up with Al MacInnis and 
the Flames in Game 3 at the Forum. LORI SHEPLER / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
