<P>
HOCKEY TEAMS; HOCKEY PLAYERS; LOS ANGELES KINGS (HOCKEY TEAM); CALGARY FLAMES 
(HOCKEY TEAM); MULLEN, LANNY; BAUMGARTNER, KEN; BUSS, JERRY 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
