A 23-year old Panorama City man was stabbed to death early Saturday morning at 
an apartment in the 14700 block of Titus Street. 
</P>
<P>
Officials said Darren Brown died at Panorama City Hospital shortly after his 
fight with a teen-age boy. They said they did not know what caused the dispute. 
</P>
</TEXT>
