<P>
Anthony Buccino, a junior at Taft High, advanced to the men's A division final 
of the American Amateur Racquetball Assn. regional singles championships in 
Santa Ana on Saturday by defeating Raymond Chinn of Torrance, 15-7, 7-15, 11-1. 
</P>
